# Take Flight with dbt and DuckDB, Dropping Dev Warehouse Costs to zero

2024/04/05

This discussion between the co-founders of Paradime and MotherDuck talks about using dbt and DuckDB to drop your warehouse development costs to zero, while eliminating sql translation between your dev and prod environments.
